#: ../../../release_details/9.5/gltf-toggle-data.md:1
msgid "GLTF document loader selectively toggle model data"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/gltf-toggle-data.md:3
msgid ""
"The `vtkGLTFDocumentLoader` learned to selectively enable/disable loading of "
"certain types of model data from the gltf file. The loader exposes the "
"following new API:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/gltf-toggle-data.md:6
msgid "`SetLoadAnimation(bool)`: Load animation keyframes (default: true)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/gltf-toggle-data.md:7
msgid "`SetLoadImages(bool)`: Load model images (default: true)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/gltf-toggle-data.md:8
msgid ""
"`SetLoadSkinMatrix(bool)`: Load inverse bind matrices for model Skin "
"(default: true)"
msgstr ""
